A song can be added to the library in a few ways, as shown below;


When &application; is first started, there will be no entries in its library. Use the Organize menu and choose Add to Library item to add songs to your library (CtrlO will do the same thing). 


Drag and drop from other applications. eg. Nautilus


Opening a song/directory in Nautilus with &application;
